# Group Activity

Access API Request Activity

## Activity [/activity{?limit,offset}]

### GetApiActivity [GET]
+ Parameters
    + limit (number, optional) -

        How many API Events should be retrieved in a single request.

        + Default: 50
        + Sample: 10
    + offset (number, optional) -

        How far into the collection of API Events should the response start

        + Default: 0
        + Sample: 50

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        OK

    + Attributes (array[APIRequest])



+ Response 401 (application/json)

        Invalid or missing token

    + Attributes (ErrorResponse)


    + Body

            {"message":"Invalid token signature","status":401}




